cu.explanation_en: Setting the GNB IPv4 address for NGU to an unreachable IP '10.0.0.1' will cause routing failure and prevent proper NGU connection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the remote N address to an unreachable IP '10.0.0.1' will cause routing failure and prevent proper F1 interface connection.
du.explanation_zh: 將遠端 N 位址設定為無法到達的 IP '10.0.0.1' 會導致路由失敗，並防止正確的 F1 介面連接。
